## 6. Authentication, Roaming and Data Profiles

### 6.1 Authentication

Algorithm: COMP128, Milenage, TUAK. Ki presence (status only). SQN for Milenage/TUAK.

### 6.2 Roaming and Regional Restrictions

| Mechanism | Layer | Effect |
|---|---|---|
| **OBR-2** | HLR ODB flags | Prevents any registration in foreign VPLMN |
| **BICROAM** | HLR SS | Bars incoming calls when roaming |
| **roamingRestriction: true** | EPS/HSS | Restriction profile applied — NOT definitive alone. Requires analysis of epsTenantId + epsRoamingAllowed |
| **epsTenantId present** | EPS/HSS | Tenant-specific restrictions apply — analyse tenant roaming profile |
| **epsTenantId absent** | EPS/HSS | Standard HSS operator restrictions apply |
| **epsRoamingAllowed: true** | EPS/HSS | ✅ Roaming permitted at EPS level |
| **epsRoamingAllowed: false** | EPS/HSS | ⛔ Roaming totally blocked at EPS level |
| **roamingAllowed: false** | IMS/HSS | Blocks IMS/VoLTE roaming |
| **Regional Subscription (LSA)** | HLR | Geographic area restrictions |

> **epsRoamingAllowed is the definitive EPS roaming parameter — not roamingRestriction alone.**

### 6.3 PS / GPRS / Data Profile

APN list, QoS (MBR, GBR, traffic class), GPRS Charging Characteristics, PDN configs for LTE/EPC.

