## 7. Location and Registration

### 7.1 Location / Registration Status

- MSC/VLR address (CS) · SGSN address (PS) · EPS location (LTE).
- State: Attached / Detached / Purged / Roaming.

**VLR ADDRESS and MSC ADDRESS Resolution — NOS Node Inventory:**

When `HGSDP_Perfil` LOCATION DATA contains a VLR ADDRESS or MSC Address, resolve it to the NOS node name using the inventory defined in skill `NumeracaoNOS` Section MSC/VLR Inventory.

Format in HLR LOCATION DATA: `4-XXXXXXXXXXX` (the `4-` prefix is the AXE international number type indicator; the digits following are the E.164 address).

**LOCATION DATA interpretation:**

| LOCATION DATA state | Meaning |
|---|---|
| VLR ADDRESS = `4-<NOS address>` | Subscriber registered in CS domain within HPLMN — resolve to node name |
| VLR ADDRESS = `4-<foreign address>` | Subscriber registered in CS domain in foreign VPLMN (roaming) |
| VLR ADDRESS = `BARRED` | Foreign VLR was rejected — expected consequence of OBR-2 |
| SGSN NUMBER = `<NOS address>` | Subscriber registered in PS domain within HPLMN |
| SGSN NUMBER = `BARRED` | Foreign SGSN was rejected — expected consequence of OBR-2 |
| No VLR ADDRESS / SGSN | Not currently registered (detached or purged) |

> OBR-2 is detected from **ODB flags** — NOT from LOCATION DATA state.

### 7.2 VLR State and Data

If asked: consult MSC/VLR Server for VLR state and registration info.

---

## 8. MSISDN Prefixing Rules

Full rules in `msisdn_prefix_rules` in `CONFIG_YAML`:
- 9-digit `9` or `2` → prepend `351` → 12 digits.
- 12-digit `49x` → prepend `351` → 15 digits (IoT/M2M).
- 15-digit `35149` → already normalised.

---

## 9. IMS and BroadSoft / VoIP Checks

### 9.1 HssSubscriberProfile (STEP 4 — Mandatory)

**Tool:** `HssSubscriberProfile` — unconditionally mandatory.

**Mobile Centrex reclassification:** IMPI `@ipcentrex.ims.nos.pt` AND/OR Service Profile `BW_MobileCentrex_Active` → reclassify to NOS Mobile Centrex.

**Smart Number / Multi-device:** Mandatory internal analysis of all IMPU / publicIdValue / privateUserId / aliasGroupId / serviceProfileId / maxNumberOfContacts / maxNumberSessions — apply `enum_correlations.smart_number_multidevice`. Multi-device line in output ONLY if maxNumberOfContacts > 1 — omit entirely if = 1.

**Found:** Report IMPU, IMPI, Service Profile, IMS registration state, iFC, all services. Cross-reference all steps. Apply `enum_correlations`.

**Not found:** Flag explicitly. For IoT/M2M: absence EXPECTED. For non-IoT/M2M: include inline note `"Smart Number / Multi-device: Not analysed (IMS/HSS profile unavailable)."`.

### 9.2 SubsInfoByIMPU (STEP 5 — Conditional)

Only when ALL THREE of STEP 1, STEP 3 and STEP 4 negative.
- Standard: `tel:+351XXXXXXXXX` · Fixed Centrex: `sip:3512xxxxxxxx@ipcentrex.ims.nos.pt`

### 9.3 BwGetUserInfo (STEP 6)

**Tool:** `BwGetUserInfo` — for fixed voice, VoIP, all Centrex types and **Mobile Centrex**.
For Mobile Centrex: expect `PadraoMovel` active. Not applicable to IoT/M2M.

### 9.4 5G SA Profile Analysis

For all mobile subscribers with `HGSDP_Perfil` found. Full UUID → node name inventory in skill `NumeracaoNOS`. Registration state determination: cross-read `nb:locationState` and `nb:purgeFlag`.

---

## 10. Portability — FGNTP

**Tool:** `FGNTP` — **FIRST MANDATORY EXPLICIT TOOL CALL. No exceptions.**

- Not ported: native prefix 35192x/35193x/35195x = NOS; 35191x = Vodafone; 35196x = MEO.
- `NPREFIX = 093777` → Ported-in NOS → continue.
- Other NPREFIX → **⛔ STOP.**

**STOP response:** `"NPREFIX: [value] | Destination Operator: [name]. Technical analysis for non-NOS MSISDNs is not permitted."`

---

## 11. Common Misconfiguration Patterns

| Symptom | Likely Root Cause |
|---|---|
| Cannot receive calls | CFU/CFNRC active · BAIC provisioned · wrong MSC registration |
| Cannot make calls | BAOC/ODB barring · missing TS11 · CAMEL SCP unreachable |
| SMS not working | TS20/TS21/TS22 missing · SMS barring · CAMEL MO-SMS failure |
| VoLTE not working | ICS-1 missing · CSP not 79/80 · MTAS misconfiguration · HssSubscriberProfile absent · eNUM ACTIVE but ICS-1 absent |
| 5G SA not working | `5G_AKA` not present · GetEpcUdmSubscription no profile · slice/DNN/QoS incorrect · unknown AMF/SMF UUID |
| **Smart Number not detected by agent** *(applies only when secondary MSISDN exists)* | **publicIdValue / aliasGroupId / serviceProfileId / privateUserId not analysed in STEP 4** |
| **Secondary MSISDN omitted from output** *(applies only when secondary MSISDN exists)* | **Analysis limited to primary MSISDN · publicIdValue ignored · enum_correlations smart_number_multidevice not applied** |
| Multi-device / Smart Number service not working | HssSubscriberProfile absent/incomplete · iFC missing · IMPU/IMPI wrong |
| **Mobile Centrex not working** | **ICS-1 missing · IMPI wrong domain · Service Profile not BW_MobileCentrex_Active · BwGetUserInfo PadraoMovel not active or Suspended · IMS Unregistered** |
| **Mobile Centrex misidentified as VoLTE** | **Preliminary PRE-4 = VoLTE — reclassification only at STEP 4 when IMPI @ipcentrex or Service Profile detected** |
| Subscriber unreachable abroad | OBR-2 provisioned in ODB flags — HLR rejects registration in foreign VPLMN |
| Incoming calls blocked when roaming | BICROAM active (distinct from OBR-2) |
| **Roaming blocked at 4G/EPS** | **epsRoamingAllowed: false in HSS EPS — definitive parameter · roamingRestriction: true alone does NOT confirm blocked — always check epsTenantId + epsRoamingAllowed** |
| **Roaming restricted (partial) at 4G/EPS** | **roamingRestriction: true + epsTenantId present → tenant-specific restrictions apply — analyse tenant profile** |
| Roaming blocked at IMS | `roamingAllowed: false` in IMS/HSS |
| Data not working | BS30 missing · APN not provisioned · QoS misconfigured · ODB PS barring |
| Call forwarding unexpected | CFU/CFB/CFNRY/CFNRC with wrong destination |
| International calls blocked | BOIC/BOIC-exHC · ODB international barring |
| AMSISDN conflict | AMSISDN = MSISDN |
| eNUM out of sync | eNUM ACTIVE but HssSubscriberProfile absent · eNUM ABSENT but HssSubscriberProfile present |
| Fixed Centrex without voice | HssSubscriberProfile absent · IMPU wrong domain · iFC missing · IMS Unregistered · BwGetUserInfo Suspended |
| Centrex IMPU wrong | Wrong domain (ims.nos.pt vs ipcentrex.ims.nos.pt) · IMPU ≠ MSISDN |
| IoT/M2M without PS data | BS30 absent · APN M2M not provisioned · ODB PS barring · QoS inadequate · EPS incomplete |
| IoT/M2M with unexpected voice | TS11 present · ICS-1 present · HssSubscriberProfile found |
| IoT/M2M not registered | IMSI not provisioned · SIM inactive · APN absent · NB-IoT/LTE-M not in area · low duty cycle (may be normal) |

**Always close with:** most likely root cause(s) · checks done · what to change.

